77 SECTION 2.
78 This Act shall become effective on July 1, 2026, only if it is determined to have been
79 concurrently funded as provided in Chapter 20 of Title 47 of the Official Code of Georgia
80 Annotated, the "Public Retirement Systems Standards Law"; otherwise, this Act shall not
81 become effective and shall be automatically repealed in its entirety on July 1, 2026, as
82 required by subsection (a) of Code Section 47-20-50.
